      {
         "id": "SECTION_introduction",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "### Introdução\n\nObserve o **Gráfico 1** a seguir:",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "markdown",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"desc\"><svg width=\"450\" height=\"100\"  fill=\"none\" stroke=\"black\"> <defs> <marker id=\"arrow\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"5\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto-start-reverse\"> <path d=\"M 0 0 L 10 5 L 0 10 z\" /></marker> </defs> <line x1=\"2\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"440\" y2=\"15\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow)\" /> <text x=\"0\" y=\"40\" font-size=\"1.5em\">0</text> <text x=\"40\" y=\"40\" font-size=\"1.5em\">1</text> <text x=\"80\" y=\"40\" font-size=\"1.5em\">2</text> <text x=\"120\" y=\"40\" font-size=\"1.5em\">3</text> <text x=\"160\" y=\"40\" font-size=\"1.5em\">4</text> <text x=\"200\" y=\"40\" font-size=\"1.5em\">5</text> <text x=\"240\" y=\"40\" font-size=\"1.5em\">6</text> <text x=\"280\" y=\"40\" font-size=\"1.5em\">7</text> <text x=\"320\" y=\"40\" font-size=\"1.5em\">8</text> <text x=\"360\" y=\"40\" font-size=\"1.5em\">9</text> <text x=\"400\" y=\"40\" font-size=\"1.5em\">10</text> <line x1=\"5\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"5\" y2=\"25\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"45\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"45\" y2=\"25\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"85\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"85\" y2=\"25\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"125\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"125\" y2=\"25\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"165\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"165\" y2=\"25\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"205\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"205\" y2=\"25\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"245\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"245\" y2=\"25\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"285\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"285\" y2=\"25\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"325\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"325\" y2=\"25\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"365\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"365\" y2=\"25\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"410\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"410\" y2=\"25\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" />  </svg></p><p class=\"desc\"><b>Gráfico 1</b>: Representação de um caminho.</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "Agora, compare com a **Figura 1**, que apresenta uma peça utilizada na cozinha da cultura Shona (<htcite0>).",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "cc162709-bdc3-469b-a208-e900f4570842",
                     "text": "Sadomba, Zvakanyorwa Wilbert",
                     "page": "",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
                        "year": "2024",
                        "month": "",
                        "day": ""
                     }
                  }
               ],
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "markdown",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"desc\"><img id=\"z0\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('z0', '0%')\" src=\"images/Zimbabue/Gourd.png\" class=\"imgcenter\"/><b>Figura 1</b>: Cabaça em um pote de cozinha do Zimbábue. Foto utilizada com autorização do doutor Zvakanyorwa Wilbert Sadomba.</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<center><div class=\"first_steps_reflection_parent\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection question_mark\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-brain\"></i></div><div class=\"first_steps_reflection\"><b>Reflexão 1: Falta algo</b><br /><br />O <b>Gráfico 1</b> mostra números espalhados ao longo de uma reta, enquanto a <b>Figura 1</b> apresenta um objeto de cozinha que é fechado em suas laterais.<br /><br />Como podemos utilizar os números para fechar os buracos no <b>Gráfico 1</b>?</div></div></center>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ]
      },
      {
         "id": "SECTION_first_idea",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "### Um primeiro passo\n\nPara melhor entendermos nossas necessidades, vamos utilizar figuras geométricas que nos auxiliem a compreender melhor o que desejamos fazer. Primeiramente, vamos desenhar um retângulo com o comprimento da reta do **Gráfico 1**.",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "markdown",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"desc\"><svg width=\"450\" height=\"140\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"black\"> <defs> <marker id=\"arrow\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"5\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto-start-reverse\"> <path d=\"M 0 0 L 10 5 L 0 10 z\" /></marker> </defs> <line x1=\"2\" y1=\"110\" x2=\"440\" y2=\"110\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow)\" /> <text x=\"0\" y=\"135\" font-size=\"1.5em\">0</text> <text x=\"41\" y=\"135\" font-size=\"1.5em\">1</text> <text x=\"82\" y=\"135\" font-size=\"1.5em\">2</text> <text x=\"123\" y=\"135\" font-size=\"1.5em\">3</text> <text x=\"164\" y=\"135\" font-size=\"1.5em\">4</text> <text x=\"205\" y=\"135\" font-size=\"1.5em\">5</text> <text x=\"246\" y=\"135\" font-size=\"1.5em\">6</text> <text x=\"287\" y=\"135\" font-size=\"1.5em\">7</text> <text x=\"328\" y=\"135\" font-size=\"1.5em\">8</text> <text x=\"369\" y=\"135\" font-size=\"1.5em\">9</text> <text x=\"405\" y=\"135\" font-size=\"1.5em\">10</text> <line x1=\"3\" y1=\"110\" x2=\"3\" y2=\"120\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"44\" y1=\"110\" x2=\"44\" y2=\"120\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"85\" y1=\"110\" x2=\"85\" y2=\"120\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"126\" y1=\"110\" x2=\"126\" y2=\"120\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"167\" y1=\"110\" x2=\"167\" y2=\"120\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"208\" y1=\"110\" x2=\"208\" y2=\"120\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"249\" y1=\"110\" x2=\"249\" y2=\"120\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"290\" y1=\"110\" x2=\"290\" y2=\"120\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"331\" y1=\"110\" x2=\"331\" y2=\"120\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"372\" y1=\"110\" x2=\"372\" y2=\"120\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"413\" y1=\"110\" x2=\"413\" y2=\"120\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <rect x=\"2\" y=\"2\" width=\"408\" height=\"95\" fill=\"lightblue\" stroke-width=\"1\"/></svg></p><p class=\"desc\"><b>Gráfico 2</b>: Representação de um retângulo sobre um caminho.</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "O retângulo sobre os números não resolve nosso problema inicial, mas pode nos conduzir a conclusões que o resolvam.",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "markdown",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<center><div class=\"first_steps_reflection_parent\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection question_mark\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-brain\"></i></div><div class=\"first_steps_reflection\"><b>Reflexão 2: Preenchendo ...</b><br /><br />Olhando para o <b>Gráfico 2</b>, como você utilizaria um retângulo (ou retângulos) para resolver nosso problema de espaços?</div></div></center>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ]
      },
      {
         "id": "SECTION_next_step",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "### Fracionando novamente\n\nO retângulo que preenche a largura de todos os números do **Gráfico 2** não resolve nosso problema de preenchimentodos valores entre os números, pois ele é maior que qualquer intervalo entre os números.\n\nSe um retângulo inteiro não resolve o problema de preenchimento, nossa solução é repetirmos o que o universo realizou e fracionar o todo (<htcite0>; <htcite1>). Comecemos olhando para nossas mãos (**Figura 1**):",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "112e532d-e8af-40d6-b1b5-527978ee42f3",
                     "text": "History Tracers Team",
                     "page": "Dois Lados",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
                        "year": "2025",
                        "month": "-1",
                        "day": "-1"
                     }
                  },
                        {
                           "type": 1,
                           "uuid": "b6f9bd52-c0cb-497e-9217-1f9677d5b491",
                           "text": "History Tracers Team",
                           "page": "Ampliando...",
                           "date_time": {
                              "type": "gregory",
                              "year": "2025",
                              "month": "",
                              "day": ""
                           }
                        }
               ],
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "markdown",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p><table class=\"book_navigation\"><tr><td>Mão esquerda</td><td>Mão direita</td></tr><tr><td><img id=\"imgLH\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgLH', '0%')\" src=\"images/HistoryTracers/Left_Hand.png\" class=\"imgcenter\"/></td><td><img id=\"imgRH\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgRH', '0%')\" src=\"images/HistoryTracers/Right_Hand.png\" class=\"imgcenter\"/></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><b>Figura 1</b>: Representação das mãos. © History Tracers. <span id=\"htImgCopyright\"></span></td></tr></table></p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "Na figura, observam-se as duas mãos de uma pessoa estendidas, com todos os dedos esticados.",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "Apesar de termos 11 números nos **Gráficos 1 e 2**. Temos 10 espaços entre os números, todos com o mesmo tamanho, que podem ser confirmados subtraindo um número do anterior:",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "markdown",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p><math display=\"block\"> <mn>1</mn> <mo>-</mo> <mn>0</mn> <mo>=</mo> <mn>1</mn> </math></p><p><math display=\"block\"> <mn>2</mn> <mo>-</mo> <mn>1</mn> <mo>=</mo> <mn>1</mn> </math></p><p><math display=\"block\"> <mn>3</mn> <mo>-</mo> <mn>2</mn> <mo>=</mo> <mn>1</mn> </math></p><p><math display=\"block\"> <mn>4</mn> <mo>-</mo> <mn>3</mn> <mo>=</mo> <mn>1</mn> </math></p><p><math display=\"block\"> <mn>5</mn> <mo>-</mo> <mn>4</mn> <mo>=</mo> <mn>1</mn> </math></p><p><math display=\"block\"> <mn>6</mn> <mo>-</mo> <mn>5</mn> <mo>=</mo> <mn>1</mn> </math></p><p><math display=\"block\"> <mn>7</mn> <mo>-</mo> <mn>6</mn> <mo>=</mo> <mn>1</mn> </math></p><p><math display=\"block\"> <mn>8</mn> <mo>-</mo> <mn>7</mn> <mo>=</mo> <mn>1</mn> </math></p><p><math display=\"block\"> <mn>9</mn> <mo>-</mo> <mn>8</mn> <mo>=</mo> <mn>1</mn> </math></p><p><math display=\"block\"> <mn>10</mn> <mo>-</mo> <mn>9</mn> <mo>=</mo> <mn>1</mn> </math></p><p class=\"desc\"><b>Cálculo 1</b>: Contagem dos números através da adição de 1.</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "Diante deste cenário, vamos dividir o retângulo do **Gráfico 2** em 10 retângulos tendo a largura 1 de comprimento:",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "markdown",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"desc\"><svg width=\"450\" height=\"140\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"black\"> <defs> <marker id=\"arrow\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"5\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto-start-reverse\"> <path d=\"M 0 0 L 10 5 L 0 10 z\" /></marker> </defs> <line x1=\"2\" y1=\"110\" x2=\"440\" y2=\"110\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow)\" /> <text x=\"0\" y=\"135\" font-size=\"1.5em\">0</text> <text x=\"41\" y=\"135\" font-size=\"1.5em\">1</text> <text x=\"82\" y=\"135\" font-size=\"1.5em\">2</text> <text x=\"123\" y=\"135\" font-size=\"1.5em\">3</text> <text x=\"164\" y=\"135\" font-size=\"1.5em\">4</text> <text x=\"205\" y=\"135\" font-size=\"1.5em\">5</text> <text x=\"246\" y=\"135\" font-size=\"1.5em\">6</text> <text x=\"287\" y=\"135\" font-size=\"1.5em\">7</text> <text x=\"328\" y=\"135\" font-size=\"1.5em\">8</text> <text x=\"369\" y=\"135\" font-size=\"1.5em\">9</text> <text x=\"405\" y=\"135\" font-size=\"1.5em\">10</text> <line x1=\"3\" y1=\"110\" x2=\"3\" y2=\"120\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"44\" y1=\"110\" x2=\"44\" y2=\"120\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"85\" y1=\"110\" x2=\"85\" y2=\"120\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"126\" y1=\"110\" x2=\"126\" y2=\"120\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"167\" y1=\"110\" x2=\"167\" y2=\"120\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"208\" y1=\"110\" x2=\"208\" y2=\"120\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"249\" y1=\"110\" x2=\"249\" y2=\"120\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"290\" y1=\"110\" x2=\"290\" y2=\"120\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"331\" y1=\"110\" x2=\"331\" y2=\"120\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"372\" y1=\"110\" x2=\"372\" y2=\"120\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"413\" y1=\"110\" x2=\"413\" y2=\"120\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <rect x=\"2\" y=\"2\" width=\"40\" height=\"95\" fill=\"lightblue\" stroke-width=\"1\"/> <rect x=\"43\" y=\"2\" width=\"40\" height=\"95\" fill=\"lightblue\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>  <rect x=\"84\" y=\"2\" width=\"40\" height=\"95\" fill=\"lightblue\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>  <rect x=\"125\" y=\"2\" width=\"40\" height=\"95\" fill=\"lightblue\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>  <rect x=\"166\" y=\"2\" width=\"40\" height=\"95\" fill=\"lightblue\" stroke-width=\"1\"/> <rect x=\"207\" y=\"2\" width=\"40\" height=\"95\" fill=\"lightblue\" stroke-width=\"1\"/> <rect x=\"248\" y=\"2\" width=\"40\" height=\"95\" fill=\"lightblue\" stroke-width=\"1\"/> <rect x=\"289\" y=\"2\" width=\"40\" height=\"95\" fill=\"lightblue\" stroke-width=\"1\"/> <rect x=\"330\" y=\"2\" width=\"40\" height=\"95\" fill=\"lightblue\" stroke-width=\"1\"/> <rect x=\"370\" y=\"2\" width=\"40\" height=\"95\" fill=\"lightblue\" stroke-width=\"1\"/></svg></p><p class=\"desc\"><b>Gráfico 3</b>: Representação de 10 retângulos sobre um caminho.</p>",
